title: For Sale:  BOBERG XR45-S .45 acp PAIR OF CONSECUTIVE SN#S 45
postcontent:
CONSECUTIVE SERIAL NUMBERS
We recently acquired this pair of New Old Stock Unfired Boberg XR45-S models with “Consecutive Serial Numbers.” The Boberg XR45-S is a mechanical work of art! This pistol utilizes a long stroke rotating barrel locked breech recoil system with dual extractors for its robustness and reliability. Boberg machines their barrels with precision tolerances allowing for equivalent and sometimes superior ballistics to common full size semi auto .45acp pistols. The locked breech rotating barrel recoil system allowed Boberg to employ a recoil buffer and slow cycle speed down by 1/3 of traditional semi autos providing substantial recoil reduction and control of the pistol. The feature that stands out above the rest is the ammunition feed system which utilizes a pull push system that pulls the round out of the magazine from the back and then pushes the round forward to chamber. The design is fascinating and fun to manipulate. Look for our two other Boberg models in the coming days. The pistols will ship with their factory box, two magazines each and documentation. There is one notable difference in the factory configuration of these pistols: one is outfitted with Tritium night sights and the other has white three dot fixed sights. Thanks for looking!
